reviewText: Yes, I had seen MIM already and can watch over and over. The other move it could happen was wonderful too, I watched it twice already. Thank you for combining the two movies together.
Who am I to rate the actual films....but the DVD? Shipping fine, quality of disc new and damage free. I happen to like these movies, so good all around! :)

Item arrived timely and as described.  "It could happen to you" is one of the best feel good films I have seen.  Highly recommended/  "Maid in Manhattan" has not been viewed yet.  Thank you, Gerald Johnson
I really like this love story and I just bought a copy to keep, so I can watch when ever I want.
